Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:33.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}創り上げて行く　真実はまだ遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:33.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}在一笔笔叙写  那真实还在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}果てない旅路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}如无尽的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:42.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}お互いのプライドを研ぎ澄ませよぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:42.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}来将各自的自尊心研磨透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:47.01,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}言葉なんて飾りは開けさせりやいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:47.01,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}敞开任何言语之类的装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:56.43,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}ぶつかり合い　磨かれていく　rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:56.43,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相互碰撞 相互摩擦 rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:59.10,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}出會いは　shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:59.10,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相遇是 shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:04.19,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}まだ知らない世界へ歩き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:04.19,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}向未知的世界迈出脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.74,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}無謀な挑戦者さ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.74,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}无谋的挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:12.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}手にした刃で明日を切り開けばいいんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:12.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}只要用手中的刀劈开明天就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.16,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}誰かのもんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.16,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}这并不是別人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}自分だけのストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}是只属于自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:31.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:23.92,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}cause we are still rough diamonds on the road!
