Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:07.06,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思えだ頃の僕は今いつーごえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:09.71,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}長い物に巻がれで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.32,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失った道しるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.96,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生ど死の狭間にわ
